      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $\\prod_{k=0}^{n-1} (\\omega ^{2k}-2\\omega ^k \\cos \\theta +1)=2(1-\\cos (n\\theta))$ avec\n$\\omega = e^{\\frac{2i\\pi}{n}}$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prod_{k=0}^{n-1} (\\omega ^{2k}-2\\omega ^k \\cos \\theta +1)=2(1-\\cos (n\\theta))\\)</span> avec <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\omega = e^{\\frac{2i\\pi}{n}}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e50abe3e-7e73-4b08-b950-bbac44578969",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\omega ^{2k}-2\\omega ^k \\cos \\theta +1 = (\\omega^k-e^{i\\theta})(\\omega^k-e^{-i\\theta})$\net $\\prod_{k=0}^{n-1}(\\omega^k-x) = (-1)^n(x^n-1)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\omega ^{2k}-2\\omega ^k \\cos \\theta +1 = (\\omega^k-e^{i\\theta})(\\omega^k-e^{-i\\theta})\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prod_{k=0}^{n-1}(\\omega^k-x) = (-1)^n(x^n-1)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
